      • lastDatasetRegistered

        public void lastDatasetRegistered(List<ch.systemsx.cisd.openbis.dss.client.api.v1.DataSet> datasets,
                                  Date lastModifiedDate,
                                  StringBuilder lastModifiedExperiment,
                                  StringBuilder lastModifiedSample)
        checks which of the datasets in the given list is the oldest and writes that into the last tree parameters Note: lastModifiedDate, lastModifiedExperiment, lastModifiedSample will be modified. if lastModifiedSample, lastModifiedExperiment have value N/A datasets have no registration dates Params should not be null
        Parameters:
        datasets - List of datasets that will be compared
        lastModifiedDate - will contain the last modified date
        lastModifiedExperiment - will contain experiment identifier, which contains last registered dataset
        lastModifiedSample - will contain last sample identifier, which contains last registered dataset, or null if dataset does not belong to a sample.
